            "titleSlug": "idempotent-matrix_23004",
            "content": "<h4 id=\"given-a-n-n-matrix-and-the-task-is-to-check-matrix-is-idempotent-matrix-or-not\">Given a N * N matrix and the task is to check matrix is idempotent matrix or not.</h4>\n\n<h4 id=\"see-the-sample-input\">See the sample input.</h4>\n\n<h4 id=\"idempotent-matrix-m-follows-the-following-property\">Idempotent matrix M follows the following property :</h4>\n\n<pre><code>M*M = M\n</code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"input-format\">Input format :</h5>\n\n<pre><code>Line 1 : Size N of the matrix\nLine 2 to N + 1 : NXN elements of the matrix\n</code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"output-format\">Output Format :</h5>\n\n<pre><code> true or false\n</code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"constraints\">Constraints :</h5>\n\n<pre><code> 1 &lt;= N &lt;= 10^3\n</code></pre>\n<h5 id=\"sample-input\">Sample Input :</h5>\n\n<pre><code>3\n2 -2 -4\n-1 3 4\n1 -2 -3\n</code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"sample-output\">Sample Output :</h5>\n\n<pre><code>true\n</code></pre>\n",
